    • getReliabilityVisualization

      public ReliabilityVisualization getReliabilityVisualization(Double m, Double e2e, String inputFileName, Integer numChannels, SystemAttributes.ScheduleChoices choice)
      This method creates a ReliabilityVisualization for testing
      Parameters:
      m - is the min packet reception rate
      e2e - is the end-to-end reliability
      inputFileName - is the input file
      numChannels - is the number of channels in the program
      choice - is the schedule to use
      Returns:
      a ReliabilityVisualization

    • getReliabilityVisualization

      public ReliabilityVisualization getReliabilityVisualization(Integer numFaults, Double m, Double e2e, String inputFileName, Integer numChannels, SystemAttributes.ScheduleChoices choice)
      This method creates a ReliabilityVisualization for testing
      Parameters:
      numFaults - is the number of faults in the WorkLoad's flows
      m - is the min packet reception rate
      e2e - is the end-to-end reliability
      inputFileName - is the input file
      numChannels - is the number of channels in the program
      choice - is the schedule to use
      Returns:
      a ReliabilityVisualization
